34 (1) time is greater than the number authorized by the license; and
35 (2) the children are maintained in a building or place not
36 designated by the license.
37 (b) A child care center may apply for licensure under this
38 chapter. If a license is issued to the child care center, the child care
39 center shall comply with state laws and rules governing licensure
40 of the child care center.
